&lt;h4 id=&#34;常用端口号&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;markdownIt-Anchor&#34; href=&#34;#常用端口号&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 常用端口号&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://kbshire-1308981697.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/img/image-20240804222100104.png&#34; alt=&#34;image-20240804222100104&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
